Package reciprocal.number.fraction

Class BigFraction

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
reciprocal.number.fraction.AbstractFraction<@NotNull BigInteger,@NotNull BigFraction,@NotNull BigDecimal>
reciprocal.number.fraction.BigFraction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<BigFraction>
public final class BigFraction extends AbstractFraction<@NotNull BigInteger,@NotNull BigFraction,@NotNull BigDecimal>
Immutable implementation of a fraction that uses BigFraction as type for its numerator and denominator

The returned Fractions of most methods are neither normalized nor reduced.

Since:
0.0.1
